vchiq_get_drvdata() wraps dev_set_drvdata() and dev_get_drvdata()
respectively.

Signed-off-by: Umang Jain <umang.jain@ideasonboard.com>
Signed-off-by: Jai Luthra <jai.luthra@ideasonboard.com>
